    <h2 style="text-align:center;">Grace: What It Is and What It Does</h2>

    <p style="text-align:center;">
      
        by <a href="brandon.html">Rev. Brandon A. Olivares</a>
      
      
        <br>(Johnstown, PA, USA)
      
    </p>
    
    
        
